# API keys loaded globally from Documents/.secrets/.env via PowerShell profile.
# Do NOT add API keys here. Use: keys set KEY value | keys reload
#
# This repo uses:
#   GEMINI_API_KEY (required) — Gemini multimodal extraction
#   ANTHROPIC_API_KEY (optional) — Claude Haiku/Sonnet text extraction
#
# No project-specific overrides needed for CKE.
